1023
00:57:47,755 --> 00:57:49,120
What does parallax view mean?

1024
00:57:49,223 --> 00:57:50,986
It's very simple.

1025
00:57:51,092 --> 00:57:54,289
It comes as close as possible
to what my position is.

1026
00:57:54,395 --> 00:57:57,091
You know that...
