moves or changes,

1030
00:58:05,973 --> 00:58:09,602
but in reality, it's just
that your perspective shifts, no?

1031
00:58:09,710 --> 00:58:14,477
Like lunar, stellar,
whatever, solar, parallax.

1032
00:58:14,582 --> 00:58:18,916
The idea is, your shift in your
subjective position is refined.

1033
00:58:19,020 --> 00:58:21,011
You perceive it
as move in the object.

1034
00:58:21,122 --> 00:58:23,215
But, of course,
then I add another twist

1035
00:58:23,324 --> 00:58:26,020
that it is in the object
in a way,

1036
00:58:26,127 --> 00:58:27,992
because object-subject
can be mediated.

1037
00:58:28,095 --> 00:58:31,929
So what interests me
is precisely this radical cut,

1038
00:58:32,033 --> 00:58:34,831
like you move from one
to another perspective.

1039
00:58:34,935 --> 00:58:39,497
There is no way
to overcome this antinomy.

1040
00:58:39,607 --> 00:58:43,099
