either you look
at your inner experience,

1044
00:58:49,417 --> 00:58:51,180
or you open the scar,

1045
00:58:51,285 --> 00:58:53,344
you see the stupid
there, brains, no?

1046
00:58:53,454 --> 00:58:55,854
But you really cannot
make the jump,

1047
00:58:55,956 --> 00:58:57,446
and you really cannot...

1048
00:58:57,558 --> 00:58:59,617
