in a relatively elaborate way,

1077
01:00:45,866 --> 01:00:48,733
like the line of thought already
written in full sentences.

1078
01:00:48,836 --> 01:00:50,895
So up to a certain point,

1079
01:00:51,005 --> 01:00:53,633
I'm telling myself, "No,
I'm not yet writing.

1080
01:00:53,741 --> 01:00:55,470
I'm just putting down ideas."

1081
01:00:55,576 --> 01:00:57,168
Then, at a certain point,

1082
01:00:57,278 --> 01:01:00,042
I tell myself, "Everything
is already there.

1083
01:01:00,147 --> 01:01:01,910
Now I just have to edit it."

1084
01:01:02,016 --> 01:01:04,450
So that's the idea,
to split it into two.

1085
01:01:04,552 --> 01:01:06,486
I put down notes, I edit it.

1086
01:01:06,587 --> 01:01:08,578
Writing disappears.

1087
01:01:11,459 --> 01:01:13,154
I'm sorry. Please.

1088
01:01:13,260 --> 01:01:14,386
Just be loud enough.

1089
01:01:23,304 --> 01:01:25,329
Good question,
but not in the sense

1090
01:01:25,439 --> 01:01:28,067
that now I will say,
"I'm modest, so nice."

1091
01:01:28,175 --> 01:01:30,166
No, it's much more serious
phenomenon.

1092
01:01:30,277 --> 01:01:31,437
Let's be quite frank.

1093
01:01:31,545 --> 01:01:34,673
At a certain superficial level,
I am relatively popular,

1094
01:01:34,782 --> 01:01:36,374
but me and my friends,

1095
01:01:36,484 --> 01:01:39,044
I don't think you can...
maybe you can...

1096
01:01:39,153 --> 01:01:44,090
