1098
01:01:46,260 --> 01:01:49,627
how many, whoever they are...

1099
01:01:49,730 --> 01:01:51,391
the enemies...

1100
01:01:51,499 --> 01:01:53,729
portray us Lacanians

1101
01:01:53,834 --> 01:01:56,598
as some kind of a phalogocentric
power discourse.

1102
01:01:56,704 --> 01:01:59,002
It's very fashionable
to paint us

1103
01:01:59,106 --> 01:02:02,701
as kind of a dogmatic
power discourse.

1104
01:02:02,810 --> 01:02:05,005
For example, yesterday,
when I delivered

1105
01:02:05,112 --> 01:02:07,205
a differently improvised version
of the same talk

1106
01:02:07,314 --> 01:02:08,474
at Columbia in New York,

1107
01:02:08,582 --> 01:02:11,949
a lady kindly towards the end
