01:02:39,613 --> 01:02:40,705
Perfect.

1111
01:02:42,016 --> 01:02:43,347
Perfect question.

1112
01:02:43,450 --> 01:02:45,145
Okay, I defy you

1113
01:02:45,252 --> 01:02:47,652
with a very simple empirical,

1114
01:02:47,755 --> 01:02:50,280
in the best Anglo-Saxon
tradition, question.

1115
01:02:50,391 --> 01:02:52,552
Apart from this brief conflict

1116
01:02:52,660 --> 01:02:55,026
between Gayatri Spivak
and Derrida,

1117
01:02:55,129 --> 01:02:57,188
