1120
01:03:02,937 --> 01:03:04,928
Name somewhere,
but name me one.

1121
01:03:05,039 --> 01:03:08,736
Why are we dogmatic?
Why are they not?

1122
01:03:08,842 --> 01:03:11,538
Name me one point

1123
01:03:11,645 --> 01:03:16,173
where Sam Weber makes an ironic critical
remark on Derrida.

1124
01:03:16,283 --> 01:03:18,683
Name me one point
where Avital Ronell does it.

1125
01:03:18,786 --> 01:03:21,346
Name me one point
where Rudolph Gasche does it.

1126
01:03:21,455 --> 01:03:24,151
So why are we...
Why is my...

1127
01:03:24,258 --> 01:03:28,490
Why am I dogmatically attached
