1132
01:03:39,239 --> 01:03:40,706
"But he's a Lacanian."

1133
01:03:40,808 --> 01:03:43,402
I am a card-carrying Lacanian.

1134
01:03:43,510 --> 01:03:45,978
Something is going on here,

1135
01:03:46,080 --> 01:03:48,378
and I just wanted to draw
the attention to this,

1136
01:03:48,482 --> 01:03:49,710
how all this popular,

1137
01:03:49,817 --> 01:03:52,911
and I think so to give you now
